content:
Suggest Replies with Einstein Service Cloud

Save agents time and create a consistent service experience. Use Einstein generative AI to create and recommend relevant replies to agents during chat and messaging sessions.

Service Replies uses Einstein generative AI to draft responses for your agents, without requiring separate model training or regular setup. In a chat, Einstein quickly drafts fluent and courteous replies based on conversation context. From the case, Einstein drafts emails based on recommended Knowledge articles. Add grounding to Service Replies to get recommendations based on your knowledge content.

Reply Recommendations without generative AI drafts replies based on your org's closed chat transcripts. No need to manually compose or search for replies. Agents can select the most relevant replies from a short list to plug in to open chats or messaging sessions.

Einstein Service Replies Increase customer satisfaction and reduce agent handling time with AI-generated replies. Einstein can generate replies during a customer chat. Or, draft and send emails based on recommended Knowledge articles, directly from the Case page.

Einstein Reply Recommendations Build a model that recommends relevant replies to support agents in the console during chat and messaging sessions. Replies are based on your Salesforce org's closed chat transcripts, and Einstein recommends replies only if you've reviewed and published them.
title: Suggesting Customer Service Responses with AI
